Budget 2025 AI Chatbot (LlamaIndex + Ollama + Local Embeddings)

This project is an **AI-powered chatbot** that allows users to ask questions about a PDF document  
 It uses:
- **LlamaIndex** for indexing PDF documents
- **HuggingFace Embeddings (`BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5`)**
- **Ollama (running locally) with Mistral LLM**
- Optional **Tkinter GUI Chat App** (desktop interface)
---


